<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Grow Your Law Practice | LegalPracticeAI</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Grow your law practice with lead management, intake forms, and analytics. Acquire and retain more clients with smart tools.">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/custom.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
                        <ol class="breadcrumb">
                            <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/" class="text-white-50">Home</a></li>
                            <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/#services" class="text-white-50">Features</a></li>
                            <li class="breadcrumb-item active text-white">Grow Your Practice</li>
                        </ol>
                    </nav>
                    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-white mb-4">Grow Your Practice</h1>
                    <p class="lead text-white-50 mb-4">Lead management, intake forms, and analytics help you acquire and retain more clients. Turn your website into a client-generating machine.</p>
                    <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                        <i class="fas fa-rocket me-2"></i>Get Started Free
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 text-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-line fa-10x text-white-50"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                    <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Tools to Grow Your Firm</h2>

                    <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body p-4">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-user-plus text-primary me-2"></i>Lead Capture</h4>
                            <p>Capture leads from your website with custom intake forms. Qualify prospects before the first call and never miss an opportunity.</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Custom intake forms for your website</li>
                                <li>Instant lead notifications</li>
                                <li>Automatic lead qualification</li>
                                <li>Integration with your marketing</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body p-4">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-funnel-dollar text-primary me-2"></i>Lead Pipeline</h4>
                            <p>Track leads through your intake process. See where prospects are in your pipeline and what actions are needed to convert them.</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Visual pipeline management</li>
                                <li>Lead scoring and prioritization</li>
                                <li>Automated follow-up reminders</li>
                                <li>Conversion tracking</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body p-4">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-door-open text-primary me-2"></i>Client Portal</h4>
                            <p>Give clients a modern experience. Secure messaging, document sharing, and case updates keep clients happy and reduce phone calls.</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>24/7 client access to case info</li>
                                <li>Secure document sharing</li>
                                <li>Online invoice payment</li>
                                <li>Reduced support calls</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body p-4">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-chart-pie text-primary me-2"></i>Business Analytics</h4>
                            <p>Understand what's working and what's not. Track lead sources, conversion rates, revenue by practice area, and more.</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Lead source attribution</li>
                                <li>Conversion rate analytics</li>
                                <li>Revenue by practice area</li>
                                <li>Marketing ROI tracking</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body p-4">
                            <h4><i class="fas fa-redo text-primary me-2"></i>Client Retention</h4>
                            <p>Keep clients coming back. Automated check-ins, satisfaction tracking, and referral programs help you build lasting relationships.</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Automated client check-ins</li>
                                <li>Satisfaction surveys</li>
                                <li>Referral tracking</li>
                                <li>Re-engagement campaigns</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-5 bg-primary text-white">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h2 class="mb-4">Ready to Grow Your Practice?</h2>
            <p class="lead mb-4">Start converting more leads into clients today</p>
            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-light btn-lg me-2">Start Free Trial</a>
            <a href="/pricing" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg">View Pricing</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
